# Code Generation Rules

## Creating New Components

```typescript
// Component file template (packages/react/src/ComponentName.tsx)
import React, { memo } from "react";
import "./ComponentName.css";

export interface ComponentNameProps {
  // Define props types
}

export const ComponentName: React.FC<ComponentNameProps> = memo((props) => {
  // Component implementation
});
```

## Creating New Utility Functions

```typescript
// Utility function template (packages/core/src/utils.ts)
/**
 * Description of the function
 * @param param Description of the parameter
 * @returns Description of the return value
 */
export const functionName = (param: Type): ReturnType => {
  // Function implementation
};
```

## Documentation Requirements

- Every exported function/component needs JSDoc comments **in English**
- Complex logic needs inline comments for explanation **in English**
- Update relevant README.md files **in English**
- Use proper English punctuation and formatting
- Maintain technical accuracy while using clear English expressions
